  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "4b5bb16eb34785407e0577ca3508a141e9fcb1e0cc2362f20a33ad7ab187d944": "It's nice to see you again, [?], and congratulations on your well deserved promotion!",
    "ac47469f6f559dcfc3249792a1a10aee083fa9b9cfaf0dcf91b1bdde1d7bc428": "What is it, [?]?",
    "994ccd78af02f0ad9bc941e42540c270ec701c62c38a1f9d62ec114c9d1b9f15": "Hello again, [?]. Do you have any news for us?",
    "bbb32a28376768373c4e8861b427bd4d5826c2cc89ce512e03de8f73bef96f45": "Not good I'm afraid, [?]. We've looked over our options and we can't see any solution to this problem. If the vampyres truly have the ability to track us then we won't be safe anywhere in Morytania.",
    "71e020e447fc34db67e204b5ad72a0bc63f2d3148f80cfe1789c224aeeff8d33": "I'm sorry, [?]. This isn't the end of our fight though. Once we're in Misthalin we can build up our strength and find more support. We'll come back stronger than ever before.",
    "9025ff4c3e1f7c7dad3099049081e8fbafb6f339c2acf062c3c4d4b1321bb351": "Because she might not have been the one to write it. [?], what was it that Verzik said about this creature Vanstrom is using?",
    "0d6cc14e41c1ce1c1cf42ee9e3d9e22bb6c7a7e7477b71337ac1ad1a39d53eb9": "Hmmm... All right. [?], work with Vertida and see if you can finish off Flaygian's work. Make no mistake though, if this doesn't come to anything then we will be leaving.",
    "0bcc7e1cd0fd72f24b1f5b2d8364124eab7b1be1c72f72476881968000b59606": "[?], you are not a citizen of Meiyerditch. You have never felt the pain that these people have. And yet, you have fought for them all the same.",
    "3e83ad41c2f9248fbf79cd2860ba593e8bc16acd2a6a747576d79260dba18b11": "Thank you, [?]. Myreque prevail.",
    "ef70b71bfe150ee94cc65ac5c1f3b2d4e7bca739919014a2d836081c8c30487d": "[?], it can never be understated what you have done today. This is the turning of the tide in our battle and it's all down to you.",
    "f7672a858dfd001e46dd13aa4c20c50633e85bfb00388c8ba4cb10459ae3ee9e": "Anyway, we'll let you get off. And once again, [?], thank you.",
    "3806a5d9dbea44f6f53ff02e67a5f29fe5118648cf71a45f5266ad706a9b5614": "Well, [?], you certainly seem to have had a very close call. Thanks for letting me know all of this. It's all highly interesting.",
    "d9fc5dc5a0fd1505a55f8d1cb9862151b55d354a97f9a7bf091eb2c30ff11927": "You've done well, [?], very well indeed. I can't decipher much of it, but from what I can tell, this tome contains research notes on the vampyres' weaknesses.",
    "baf78932b0225e05693c08a9b97244f22ebdffa4f0f710083cbf7f3fef252937": "I can believe that, [?]. Once again you have our gratitude. For my part, your arrival has not come soon enough. I have a feeling that your efforts in our struggle are not yet over.",
    "42cd165a9d27f43be0a56888b5aabcfc85b119794b0292749c2c17ccb3a5299c": "Indeed. And [?], good to see you as well. Myreque prevail.",
    "14fc1b746e625e6db42fe39a6684a805ea0121d8b8c672bf72b6ecd4f7b45335": "Well I won't pretend this isn't risky. But I have faith in [?], here. The first human to kill a vyre, and quite the vyre it was. Vanescula would be unwise to try anything.",
    "dc93c15cbde7115abc0f1a86251e79e9b7629b732dfe1342aa37df150be1681e": "Ah, of course. [?], after due consideration by Veliaf and I, we would like to promote you to the rank of lieutenant in the Myreque. Congratulations!",
    "fd5764005b1340dc357bdb39f725d9fe4f5e70a11775150097a2939d44aae009": "Any luck with the lock, [?]?",
    "7f528dc5dd1cd049254bc0cf66d6ea82f0f39c4ed399f9a0e73cb76ee86bd605": "[?], I need some time to think over what we have discovered here. Please, inform the others for me.",
    "819fa24390d6c7a1d50081d5e41fcc0d0464b68ac454fd422e44ec2ad7955e7d": "I would like to join you, [?].",
    "61af6546b14c733c3b17dc825dea4fd674eb85a55000d7ea846e961c301e68f7": "[?], do you remember how to reach the laboratory?",
    "c8270cd4774fce4f83d2123072c85bdcba47ba33503708e2ded70adad042f5c8": "Good to see you, [?]. Glad you made it here safely.",
    "1274ee145190de43094556e52114e980fbfbd7e59948489bb0a6e79d0acf4017": "Bah, look at me, [?]. I'm meant to be a leader, but I can barely control my own body. I'm like an old man.",
    "1bb993e73227f2abcc737c81ee03922501e5cb3c5dc6d5d5e7b9ad5c884988a2": "Come now, [?]. We need that research. Please give it to me as soon as you can.",
    "06458c2d7153eb698440a39268b640c83ed8aa1b8393b6c6b490bc69a5c6248e": "Good idea. [?], could you pick up a vyrewatch disguise from Trader Sven? He lives in sector one of Meiyerditch, directly south of Old Man Ral's house.",
    "015b7e690052ab099c4f746b21ae0315b10256afb7ff0959527c15f4c13d892e": "[?]. It suits you, [?].",
    "e40a1453356e955868e4f97c9d6e417bd6f1c92bd03a26a69cff0eebe6e76730": "Good luck [?]. Myreque prevail.",
    "de45c3564802fbc612eb9968b4758bfd05ece0eb43f9de202773594aa8905edc": "Oh... One last thing, [?].",
    "eb24e2138cb38f72714e28def55175fc505923663c6a10020bdf58775084916f": "Make sure you're ready for this, [?]. Once we start, there's no going back."
  }
}